        public double rideCost(long time,
                       Bicycle bicycle)
        Description copied from class: Card
        there's three way to compute the cost of a ride depending of the card possessed by the user. VLIBRE_Card and VMAX_Card does override rideCost. The default way is corresponding to an absence of card, NoCard does not override rideCost. the cost is 1 Euro per hour (for mechanical bikes) and 2 Euro per hour (for electrical bikes)
